  "Description": {
    "English": "A reactive element most easily harvested by processing the salt-infused minerals found in <span class=\"name name-technology\">oceans</span>.<br><br>Used in the manufacture of advanced technologies.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种反应性元素，加工<span class=\"name name-technology\">海洋</span>中的盐类矿物即可轻易收获。<br><br>用于制造先进技术。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种反应性元素，加工<span class=\"name name-technology\">海洋</span>中的盐类矿物即可轻易收获。<br><br>用于制造先进技术。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "活性元素，最簡單的收集方法就是加工處理<span class=\"name name-technology\">海洋</span>中蘊含鹽分的礦物。<br><br>製作先進科技時能派上用場。"
  },
